### 正常：主题分页
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-topics-normal

### 参数错误：非法编码和颜色
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-topics-invalid

{"code":"非法 编码","name":"","color":"blue","language":"zh-CN","enabled":true,"sortOrder":0}

### 记录不存在
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics/999999
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-topics-not-found

### 状态冲突：删除已关联来源的主题（替换 ID）
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics/1
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-topics-conflict
